[
  {
    "startTime": 7.68,
    "endTime": 9.5,
    "text": "Hi Bob the Canadian here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.5,
    "endTime": 11.95,
    "text": "Let's talk about noses."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.95,
    "endTime": 13.899999999999999,
    "text": "Everyone has one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.9,
    "endTime": 18.4,
    "text": "Mine's a little bit bigger than most."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.4,
    "endTime": 20.229999999999997,
    "text": "Hi Bob the Canadian here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.23,
    "endTime": 28.47,
    "text": "Today I wanted to talk a little bit about those little things that you can say to help you during an English conversation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.47,
    "endTime": 34.849,
    "text": "So let's say you're having a conversation with someone and they're talking about something that you find interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.1,
    "endTime": 41.480000000000004,
    "text": "A neat way to make the conversation flow better is to say things like: That's neat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.48,
    "endTime": 42.199999999999996,
    "text": "Or..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.2,
    "endTime": 43.489000000000004,
    "text": "That's cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.489,
    "endTime": 44.199999999999996,
    "text": "Or..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.2,
    "endTime": 45.800000000000004,
    "text": "That's interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.8,
    "endTime": 53.55,
    "text": "And if you need some time to think you can even stretch it out and say things like: I find that interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.55,
    "endTime": 55.73,
    "text": "I find that pretty neat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.73,
    "endTime": 58.19,
    "text": "I find that fascinating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.19,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "Another suggestion to help conversation with English speakers go better is to simply ask them questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 67.898,
    "text": "People love talking about themselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.899,
    "endTime": 72.3,
    "text": "So if you can ask questions like: How many times did you do it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.3,
    "endTime": 74.14,
    "text": "How long were you gone for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.14,
    "endTime": 74.8,
    "text": "Or..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.8,
    "endTime": 76.38,
    "text": "Did you enjoy yourself?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.38,
    "endTime": 80.8,
    "text": "Or...Describe that to me a bit. It sounds fascinating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.8,
    "endTime": 82.86,
    "text": "Which leads me to the last example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.86,
    "endTime": 84.52,
    "text": "You can combine the two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.52,
    "endTime": 92.119,
    "text": "So you'll want to get comfortable saying things like: That's neat. I find that fascinating. How long were you gone for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.119,
    "endTime": 93.119,
    "text": "Or..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.119,
    "endTime": 96.56,
    "text": "That's really interesting. So you like camping?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.56,
    "endTime": 97.659,
    "text": "Or..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.659,
    "endTime": 105.24000000000001,
    "text": "I find that pretty neat. I've always wanted to do that. Was it hard to get started?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.24,
    "endTime": 106.6,
    "text": "Bob the Canadian here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.6,
    "endTime": 108.309,
    "text": "Learn English with Bob the Canadian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.31,
    "endTime": 112.59,
    "text": "I'm really enjoying making these videos for you and I hope you're enjoying watching them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.59,
    "endTime": 114.619,
    "text": "Please subscribe below to my channel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.619,
    "endTime": 117.2,
    "text": "I'm trying to make a video at least once a week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.2,
    "endTime": 118.2,
    "text": "Sometimes more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.2,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "And it's my job to help you learn English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 122.119,
    "text": "Have a great day."
  }
]